===Etymology===

''Vittu'' appears to be very original Finnish. The only nearby language with a similar word for ''vittu'', is [[Swedish]], ''fitta''. If it was adopted to Swedish from [[German]], English would probably have a very similar word for it too. 

On the other hand, Swedish has ''ficka'' for pocket, and this could be a loose relation to [[vagina]]. The German verb ''ficken'', "to fuck", could then be related. 

